            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Each tool uses different data sources and estimation methods — Google Keyword Planner, Ahrefs, Semrush, and Moz produce varying results for the same keyword. Consistency within one tool matters more than comparing absolute numbers across platforms.</p></div></div>
